1.title: Make Up School
1.plot: We go beyond the runways, and head on to the heart of London's creative hub, Soho. Let's check out one of the most sought-after schools for aspiring makeup artists, AOFM Pro, as they open their doors to us for a premiere internship program experience for our very own Stefanie Rycraft Jones.

2.title: Millinery
2.plot: The art of hat making in the Western culture goes back as far as the late 14th century, emerging as an essential status symbol for men and for women in the later part of the century. Stefanie goes behind the closed doors of British luxury milliner - Alexandra Harper, and join us as we take a look at an internship experience at her millinery shop in London.

3.title: AEVHA London
3.plot: Handbags and purses have already been used since the earliest time of civilization. At the present day, exclusive designers' handbags have become important accessories for women's fashion; And with women as the most influential factor, the designs and variety of handbags are now changing season after season. Stefanie will be taking us behind the scene of a luxury handbag British company, AEVHA London, for an internship experience at their fabulous Mayfair showroom.

imdb.title: Fashion Underground
plot: An inside look at some of the industry's hottest internships. Spending a day in a the life of an intern and discover what your dream job in fashion is all about.::Fashion One International LLC.
